Start the game:
	Press "Play"
	Press "Join" or "Host"
	Enter necessary information to join or host a game
	If hosting, select the number of players
	Connect and continue to the game
Play the game:
	Each turn you can pass or play a word
	You can swap as many tiles as many times as you would like
	The first word of a game must include the middle tile
	Each word must be a valid word in the English language
	Each letter has a point value
	The points add up to your score for each word
	The game ends when all players pass twice in a row
	BONUS: You may randomly get one extra letter
Play a letter:
	Click the letter you want to move from your rack
	Click the tile on the board you want to move that letter to
Objective: 
	End the game with the most points